there are 7 steps to launch an instance

select EC2 service--------->select instances--->launch instance-->give instance name------>select type of OS like amazon, ubuntu, windows etc as per requirement
(select free tier )-------> select instance type here (select free tier )---------> create key pair----->create security group------>here configuration storage is free
upto 30GB-----> launch instance

